===Noun===
'''お姉さん''' ([[おねえさん]], ''[[onēsan]]'')

# (Honorific): One's older sister.  Used as term of address to one's own older sister, and to refer to other people's older sisters.  

===Synonyms===
* '''[[姉]]''' ([[あね]], ''[[ane]]''): (Humble): Used to refer to one's own older sister when talking to someone else.

